85
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,580
Uh... Chen...

86
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:16,300
Chen Chui Bao

87
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:19,280
Chen Chui Bao. To je skutočné meno?

88
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:20,780
Nepamätám sa.

89
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,920
Kde teraz je?

90
00:06:25,780 --> 00:06:26,440
Neviem.

91
