Rada ťa spoznávam.

102
00:07:01,300 --> 00:07:02,860
Wow, tento internát je skvelý.

103
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,040
Ahoj.

104
00:07:10,900 --> 00:07:11,900
Qing Qing.

105
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:14,520
Priniesla si si len túto tašku?

106
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:15,240
Áno.

107
00:07:16,020 --> 00:07:18,200
Ako budeš spať bez obliečok?

108
00:07:19,755 --> 00:07:22,265
Neposkytne to škola?

109
00:07:22,415 --> 00:07:24,265
Škola ti to nedá.

110
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:27,160
Čo keby som to s tebou
neskôr išla kúpiť?

111
00:07:27,220 --> 00:07:27,980
Dobre.

112
00:07:27,980 --> 00:07:29,980
Odpočiň si.

113
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:42,500
Fang Fang.

114
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:44,660
Qing Qing, vybrala si si niečo?

115
